  "rationale": "<p>Treating x\u00b2 as a variable, factor x<sup>4</sup> \u2212 5x\u00b2 \u2212 14 as (x\u00b2 \u2212 7)(x\u00b2 + 2). Check: (x\u00b2 \u2212 7)(x\u00b2 + 2) = x<sup>4</sup> + 2x\u00b2 \u2212 7x\u00b2 \u2212 14 = x<sup>4</sup> \u2212 5x\u00b2 \u2212 14. \u2713 Choice (a) is correct.</p>",
